  "detailed_description": "<h1>Special Offer</h1><p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1052360/extras/975fae557865a50b100a1c6ef0a7afd5.avif?t=1628307519\" width=616 height=250 /></span><br>Owners of Tzompantli on Steam automatically unlock exclusive character Evangeline as a playable character for Combate Monero!</p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>Combate Monero is and indie fighting game where different mexican comic book characters duke it out in combat. Sequel to our earlier game, Tzompantli, the fighting system is similar, with a fluid and dinamic style.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1052360/extras/426958375f743eef142d5c45e8738d63.poster.avif?t=1628307519\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1052360/extras/426958375f743eef142d5c45e8738d63.webm?t=1628307519\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1052360/extras/426958375f743eef142d5c45e8738d63.mp4?t=1628307519\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>24 Fighters from a diversity of Mexican Indie comic Books, like Meteorix, Jours de Papier, el Bulbo, Zeraky and more!<br></li><li>Cell Shaded Graphics with vibrant colors and varied and original characters<br></li><li>Dynamic combat system inpired in Guilty gear and Other anime fighters<br></li><li>Classic Arcade mode with and end boos battle<br></li><li>Arcade and Training Mode for one or two players<br></li><li>customizable Controls<br></li><li>Original Soundtrack by Jake Wayne<br></li><li>New Fighters will join the roster periodically, and Free!<br></li><li>New game modes will be added as well<br></li><li>Made with Unity and teh UFE library!</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1052360/extras/8db206d711162633da22fa62a5270f9a.poster.avif?t=1628307519\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1052360/extras/8db206d711162633da22fa62a5270f9a.webm?t=1628307519\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1052360/extras/8db206d711162633da22fa62a5270f9a.mp4?t=1628307519\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The controller is fully supported in menus and gameplay, but not in the game Launcher.",
